Q_DESC:
Virat Kohli has won the toss against Australia in a 50 Over World Cup Final 2019.  During the Toss time the commentator have him a funny task to test his mathematical skills. 

Shastri was the umpire to judge his mathematical skills. When the number is 23 he needs tell INDIA  and when the number is 50 he needs to tell AUSSIE.

When the number is less than  0 he needs to tells as Sorry. Help our cricket captain by writing a sample program.

Refer sample Input and Output:
Input 1: 20 Output: AUSSIE
Input 2: 21 Output: INDIA 
Input 3: 22 Output: AUSSIE
Input 4: -1 Output: Sorry
